oads/2024/03/olivia-rodrigo-sheryl-crow-jason-kempin-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/olivia-rodrigo-sheryl-crow-jason-kempin-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/olivia-rodrigo-sheryl-crow-jason-kempin-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/olivia-rodrigo-sheryl-crow-jason-kempin-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/olivia-rodrigo-sheryl-crow-jason-kempin-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>邀请谢丽尔·克劳<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sheryl-crow">(Sheryl Crow)</a>在纳什维尔表演《如果这让你快乐》(If It Makes You Happy)。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) – 《胆量》评论：流行音乐的轰动确保了她作为一代天才的地位</a></strong></li></ul><p>罗德里戈目前正在进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-2024-guts-world-tour-shows-buy-tickets-3497458">她的“GUTS”世界巡演的北美站</a>，并与 Crow 一起表演了“我最喜欢的歌曲之一”，Crow 是巡演的第一位惊喜嘉宾。</p><p>这并不是两人第一次二重唱，他们之前曾于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-sheryl-crow-sing-if-it-makes-you-happy-3507325">9 月在纳什维尔的蓝鸟咖啡馆 (Bluebird Cafe) 的一次亲密演出</a>中合作表演，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sheryl-crow-perform-with-olivia-rodrigo-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-2023-3530414">于 11 月</a>Crow 入选摇滚名人堂时再次合作。</p><p>查看以下由粉丝拍摄的表演片段：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">神啊！奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 演唱谢丽尔·克劳 (Sheryl Crow) 演唱的歌曲“If It Makes You Happy” <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/GUTSWorldTourNashville?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#GUTSWorldTourNashville</a><br /> <a href="https://t.co/R1Tryh7tre">pic.twitter.com/R1Tryh7tre</a></p><p> — 奥利维亚·罗德里戈·巴西 (@oliviarodrigobr) <a href="https://twitter.com/oliviarodrigobr/status/1766672666021224747?ref_src=twsrc%5E